            <p><strong>Material Cost:</strong> $28.45</p>
            <p><strong>Labor Cost:</strong> $6.00</p>
            <p><strong>Misc Loss:</strong> $1.00</p>
            <p><strong>Total Loaded Cost:</strong> $35.45</p>
            <p><strong>Net Profit:</strong> $45.00</p>
        </div>
    </div>

